snippet.title: Slash Out Arcade
snippet.description:
This game is third installment to the Spikeout series.
Unlike other games in the series, Slashout has a completely different setting, based in a fantasy world with different characters—gameplay remains similar, however.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/InsertCoinArcadeOfficial/
